<div class="container">
  <h1>Order Pickup</h1>
  <p>To comply with social distancing guidelines and to ease the burden of cleaning up, this year we are hosting pick up times for orders. Your earliest pickup window depends on when you placed the order. 
  <p>Orders placed <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Friday thru Monday</span> will be avaliable for pickup <span style="text-decoration: underline;">the following Wednesday, 6pm to 8pm.</span>.<br/>Orders placed <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Tuesday thru Thursday</span> will be avaliable for pickup <span style="text-decoration: underline;">the following Saturday , 6pm to 8pm.</span>. <br/>If you miss <span style="text-decoration: underline;">three pickup times</span> after your order is placed, <span style="text-decoration: underline;">expect a phone call reminder regarding your order.</span></p>
	<div class="col-md-8 order-md-1">
      <h4 class="mb-3">Billing address</h4>
      <form action="/process_user" method="POST">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
            <label for="firstName">First name</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="firstName" name="fname" placeholder="" value = <%= @fname %>>
            <div class="invalid-feedback">
              Valid first name is required.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
            <label for="lastName">Last name</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="lastName" name="lname" placeholder="" value = <%= @lname %>>
            <div class="invalid-feedback">
              Valid last name is required.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" value = <%= @email %>>
          <div class="invalid-feedback">
            Please enter a valid email address.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="address">Address</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="address" name="line1" placeholder="1234 Main St" value = <%= @line1 %>>
          <div class="invalid-feedback">
            Please enter your shipping address.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="address2">Address 2 <span class="text-muted">(Optional)</span></label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="address2" name="line2" placeholder="Apartment or suite" value = <%= @line2 %>>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
            <label for="zip">City</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="city" name="city" placeholder="" value = <%= @city %>>
            <div class="invalid-feedback">
              City required.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
            <label for="zip">Zip</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="zip" name="zip" placeholder="" maxlength="5" value= <%= @zip %> >
            <div class="invalid-feedback">
              Zip code required.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <%= @shipping_option %>
      <input type="submit" value="Proceed to Payment">

	</form>
</div>
</div>